Adeola "Ade" Dagunduro (ka amụrụ na Mee 22, 1986) bụ onye Naijiria na Amerịka lara ezumike nká na-egwu egwuregwu basketball.
Mgbe ọ gụsịrị basketball ụlọ akwụkwọ sekọndrị na Inglewood High, Dagunduro wee gbaa basketball kọleji na Mt
San Antonio College (2004–05), Antelope Valley CC (2005–07), na Mahadum Nebraska, ebe ya na Nebraska Cornhuskers (2007–09).
N'oge ọ na-egwu egwu, Dagunduro na Mitteldeutscher BC nke German League, Leuven Bears nke Belgian League, na Virtus Roma nke Italian League.
Dagunduro nọchitere anya Naịjirịa na 2012 Summer Olympics
